text: Sigurður Ingi Jóhannsson (born 20 April 1962) is an Icelandic politician. He was the Prime Minister of Iceland from April 2016 to January 2017. He is the chairman of the Progressive Party. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Sigurdur Ingi Johannsson
title: Sigurður Ingi Jóhannsson
